Dream2Pieces
The Lego Box

by Iam Curio

*********************************

Dear Diary:

Tomorrow is my birthday and I can barely sleep.  My present is very well hidden somewhere in this house.

I have been talking to my mom for months about what I would like to get for my birthday.

There was a new lego set box coming out and I wanted to have it as soon as possible. So, i'm counting on it.

Well, now, I should be counting something else like sheep to try to sleep...

*********************************

Barn
I was in my bedroom but I'm pretty sure that I'm dreaming now. My first clue? Well, everything is made of lego, walls, ceiling and floor.  And just look at me, I'm a figurine!

And about my second clue... I woke up in the family barn for some reason. I do enjoy playing with animals made of lego.  They are not alive after all and there is no chance for me to die from a kick anyway.

Should I ask for help?  I don't even see a way out. I'll have to make one of lego.  So, let's get to it.
There is a horse in the corner.
There is also a donkey here.

I can play with a HORSE and a DONKEY.

> BREAK and MIX legos to make objects.
> break horse

> break horse

