Backyard
Oh! This is probably one of those dreams where you wake up and feel some relief.  But then you realize that you are still dreaming.  A dream inside another dream.  I shouldn't eat so much candy just before going to bed.

I'm now in the backyard.  My mom sometimes leaves the backdoor unlocked.  Let's hope I'm lucky enough to find it.
There is a pool in the middle of the backyard.
I can see a duck from here.

I can play with a POOL and a DUCK.

