"I grew in an old farm with my grandma before moving to the city.  It was fun to climb the trees and explore all kind of places.

But my favorite hobbie was looking for secret doors in the house.  I was convinced that it should be one secret door, like in those old castles from tv.

So, I used to look under the bed, shelves, basically everywhere.  I never found it but I never lost hope.

I guess all of that was my natural instinct for escaping from things.  Specially the ones that I liked the most, believe it or not."

