Game Room
My favorite place in the whole house where there are all my toys.  The time flies when I'm here without me noticing it.  I play chess and throw darts here all the time.  The game room is full of puzzles. This must be the trickiest and probably the last door I'll have to create.
I can see some darts scattered around.
Last time I played chess I threw the rook to the floor.
There is a clock in the wall ticking...
There is a board in the middle of the room.

I can play with a DARTS, a ROOK, a CLOCK and a BOARD.

> break darts

> break darts

