I didn't see this one coming.
> enter hole

> enter hole
"As I was falling through the hole slowly like Alice in Wonderland I had a moment of enlightenment.  I felt suddenly that I was not only a character in this dream.  I was something else.  Another piece in a bigger puzzle and someone was playing it, making the decisions instead of me.  I was no longer sure if I was real or not.

And then I opened my eyes for the first time and I saw it.  In front of me there was a wall.  On the wall there was a message.  I looked up and started reading it.  It said:  "As I was falling through the hole...".   I stop reading realizing those were my thoughts being printed somehow by a strange force.  Then everything became clear.  This wasn't a dream, it was a game, a computer game.  I turned around and I saw a big screen.  Beyond the screen there was a face looking at me.  Well, not me.  Looking at the wall behind me, reading my thoughts.   I said "Hello" but no sound came out of me.

Finally, I touched the bottom of the hole and closed my eyes again forgetting the strange experience that I just had."

