Dear Diary:

My mom didn't forget! How can she anyway, after me talking about it all the time? I received my Evil Scientific Machine Lego Tool Set!!! I can't believe it's finally here. Today I worked hard to put everything together, and it is now sitting in my chair. Looking at it from my bed while writing this journal makes me wonder about the strange dream I had last night. I guess our wishes are the power and fuel for our dreams. If I have another one I'll be sure to write it down to share with my friends. So, my friend from the other side of the screen, if you are reading this right now...

CONGRATULATIONS. YOU HAVE WON!!!

THE END

